{"code":0,"message":"","data":null,"sentence":{"phonemes":[],"text":"I hate eating mushrooms. I hate mushrooms in my pizza. I hate mushrooms in my burgers. I hate mushrooms in my soup. I hate mushrooms in my fried rice. I hate mushrooms in my buns. I hate mushrooms in my dumplings. Mushrooms can be chopped so small they're barely visible, but their scent seeps into every single grain of rice.","words":[]}}
